com.enremmeta.rtb

Class BidCandidate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.enremmeta.rtb.BidCandidate

  • public final class BidCandidate
extends Object
    Represents an Ad during the process of a bid request and keeps track of which aspects of this Ad pass the bid request and internal restrictions, and therefore will be allowed to be returned to the exchange with the bid, and which will not.
    Author:
    Gregory Golberg (grisha@alum.mit.edu)
